{"tid":1316000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我只想講一樣嘢，唔撚好再拉低口罩","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:44:34.000Z","uid":227968,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"633d29e352653ab4a725d5c64f06cfea6727f48d","tid":1316000,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\">今日全日喺屋企睇live </span><br />\n見到好多人幫手大嗌要物資要剩<br />\n我都知口罩又吸聲又易移位，<br />\n你就拉撚低口罩嗌<br />\n飲水又拉撚低<br />\n見到啲人咁樣真係好危險，好易比人捕到你全相<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">嗌人唔好影冇用</span>，大撚把高處偷偷影都好易<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，重點嚟喇<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好再貪靚樣，<br />\n所有唔想做和理非都比人偷影到嘅<br />\n去花園街女人街行山用舖頭，<br />\n買返以下呢樣嘢<br />\n全民必備！<br />\n遮髮型、面型、頸、耳，<br />\n又防曬防蚊，又防不明噴霧偷襲，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>總之除咗對眼，成個外貌特徵根本遮撚哂！</strong></span></span><br />\n又透氣舒服，<br />\n再唔全民學識保護自己，就真係抵你比人起底喇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請參閱以下附件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAHSB53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAHSB53.png&h=7b72e602&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1gPEjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1gPEjp.png&h=14ff06aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgtymxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgtymxL.png&h=839ce94e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0df14468e82bffa7865bc63bc970ed2a5f1aac17","tid":1316000,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67c85c0b753ec94c653c6a469f40d83d70d2ba44","tid":1316000,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"唔該你哋"},{"pid":"2315a300f06b7a8e1ea3d0983cde0ae3771a7427","tid":1316000,"uid":227968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fe376c29f0b691b3c882a22d17488331e48e0b4","tid"